OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1772460676
OL,3,CSchool children's work displayed in
OL,4,Cexhibition alongside famous art
OL,6,FThe work of school children from West
OL,7,FCumbria has been put on display in an
OL,8,Fexhibition dedicated to JD Kenworthy.
OL,10,FKenworthy was an Edwardian artist from
OL,11,FWhitehaven famous for his self
OL,12,Fportraits and paintings of Cumbrian
OL,13,Fpeople.
OL,15,FMany pieces of his work are now on
OL,16,Fdisplay at the Beacon Museum in
OL,17,FWhitehaven alongside art from pupils
OL,18,Fof St James' Junior School in the town.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
