PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1772460676
OL,3,CSchool children's work displayed in
OL,4,Cexhibition alongside famous art
OL,6,FThey have been learning about him and
OL,7,Fhis work and have created their own
OL,8,Fpieces of art after being inspired by
OL,9,Fhim.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV Border, Alex Whitworth
OL,12,Fspoke of the importance of encouraging
OL,13,Fthe next generation to explore their
OL,14,Flove for art.
OL,16,FShe said: "Often I think that people
OL,17,Fthink that younger audiences aren't
OL,18,Fparticularly interested in galleries
OL,19,Fand museums and they don't realise it
OL,20,Fis for them as well because they are
OL,21,Four audiences of the future.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1772460676
OL,3,CSchool children's work displayed in
OL,4,Cexhibition alongside famous art
OL,6,F"I think going into a gallery as a
OL,7,Fyoungster is really important, they
OL,8,Fcan see the connections between going
OL,9,Fto a gallery and how it is relevant to
OL,10,Fthem.
OL,12,F"It gives them that incite into what
OL,13,Fhe was doing. Bearing in mind he was
OL,14,Fsomeone who worked locally there is
OL,15,Falso this sense of pride.
OL,17,F"You think he painted brilliantly and
OL,18,Fonly lived down the road. It also
OL,19,Fgives them something to aspire to as
OL,20,Fwell."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
