PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1772460676
OL,3,CSchool children's work displayed in
OL,4,Cexhibition alongside famous art
OL,6,FJD Kenworthy specialised in self-
OL,7,Fportraits and painting Cumbrian people
OL,8,Ffrom mayors to doctors and farmers.
OL,10,FAlan Gillon from the Beacon Museum
OL,11,Fexplained the challenges they have in
OL,12,Fidentifying all of the people painted
OL,13,Fby Kenworthy.
OL,15,FHe said: "It is like one massive
OL,16,Fjigsaw puzzle and occasionally we have
OL,17,Fmissing pieces but we don't know how
OL,18,Fthey fit into the puzzle.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
