CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1772460676
OL,3,CSchool children's work displayed in
OL,4,Cexhibition alongside famous art
OL,6,F"If anyone can tell us about these
OL,7,Fpeople in the paintings by Kenworthy
OL,8,Fthen that would be fantastic."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/5
